{{notability|Music|date=March 2015}} {{unreferenced|date=March 2015}} {{Infobox song | name = We Are All God's Children | artist = [[Jamie Rivera]] with the Hail Mary the Queen Children's Choir | type = single | album = We Are All God's Children | released = 2014 | format = [[Compact disc|CD]], [[Music download|digital download]] | recorded = 2014 | genre = [[Gospel music|Gospel]] | length = 3:35 | label = [[Star Music]] | composer = Noel Diño Espenida | lyricist = Jaime Rivera | producer = Jamie Rivera }}
"We Are All God's Children" is a 2014 [[Gospel music|Gospel]] song composed by Noel Diño Espenida with lyrics written and performed by [[Jamie Rivera]]. The song was used as the theme of the [[Pope Francis's visit to the Philippines|Papal Visit of Pope Francis to the Philippines]].
==Production== *Lead vocals: [[Jamie Rivera]] with the Hail Mary the Queen Children's Choir *Lyrics: Jamie Rivera *Composed and arranged: Noel Diño Espenida *Produced: Jamie Rivera
